OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,FA driver who took "at least 20 lines
OL,7,Fof cocaine" in the hours before he hit
OL,8,Fa tram and then collided with a three-
OL,9,Fyear-old girl on a pavement has been
OL,10,Fjailed for 12 years.
OL,12,FLouisa Palmisano, known as Lulu, died
OL,13,Fin hospital from her injuries after
OL,14,Fshe was struck on Booth Street in
OL,15,FManchester, while holding hands with
OL,16,Fher parents on a family visit on 22
OL,17,FFebruary.
