OL,3,CDriver who 'recklessly' drove after
OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,FRawal Rehman, who had spent the
OL,7,Fevening at massage parlours, pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to causing her death by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving in his Mercedes
OL,10,FSprinter van.
OL,12,FThe 36-year-old, from Manchester, then
OL,13,Ffled the scene of the collision in a
OL,14,Ftaxi at about 10am where police later
OL,15,Ftraced him using documents found in
OL,16,Fhis van, arresting him two days later.
