OL,3,CDriver who 'recklessly' drove after
OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,FRehman was sentenced to 12 years in
OL,7,Fjail at Manchester Crown Court, and
OL,8,Fdisqualified from driving for more
OL,9,Fthan 13 years, by Judge Alan Conrad KC
OL,10,Fwhen he appeared on 27 May.
OL,12,FAbbie Clarke, Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,13,Ffor CPS North West, said Rehman's
OL,14,Factions "caused absolute devastation".
OL,16,F"Rawal Rehman was in no fit state to
OL,17,Fdrive that morning, yet he recklessly
OL,18,Fchose to get behind the wheel of his
OL,19,Fvan after a cocaine binge," she said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
