OL,3,CDriver who 'recklessly' drove after
OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,F"His actions have caused absolute
OL,7,Fdevastation for one family and shocked
OL,8,Four entire community.
OL,10,F"Rawal Rehman ignored the stop signs
OL,11,Fand tram warning signs when he drove
OL,12,Fstraight into the path of an oncoming
OL,13,Ftram.
OL,15,F"After the collision, Rehman fled the
OL,16,Fscene in a taxi, not willing to face
OL,17,Fthe consequences of his selfish
OL,18,Factions. He now faces a hefty
OL,19,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
