OL,3,CDriver who 'recklessly' drove after
OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,F"Today our thoughts are with Lulu's
OL,7,Ffamily ` and we hope the sentence
OL,8,Fhanded down offers them some solace as
OL,9,Fthey mourn the tragic loss of their
OL,10,Fyoung daughter."
OL,12,FThe court previously heard that Rehman
OL,13,Fhad visited two massage parlours in
OL,14,Fthe city in the early hours of
OL,15,FFebruary 22 and had taken "at least 20
OL,16,Flines of cocaine" in seven hours.
OL,18,FCCTV of the incident was played to the
OL,19,Fcourt, showing the family walking
OL,20,Falong the pavement, with Lulu between
OL,21,Fher parents, holding their hands.
