OL,3,CDriver who 'recklessly' drove after
OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,FRehman failed to stop at the junction,
OL,7,Fdespite large stop signs and warnings
OL,8,Fwritten on the road.
OL,10,FThe side of his van was then hit by an
OL,11,Foncoming tram, forcing his vehicle on
OL,12,Fto the pavement and into the family,
OL,13,Fknocking the parents aside.
OL,15,FRehman, who had his hood up, got out
OL,16,Fof the van and walked around the
OL,17,Fvehicle before retrieving his phone
OL,18,Fand leaving the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
