OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,FIn 2017, Rehman was jailed for three
OL,7,Fyears for conspiracy to pervert the
OL,8,Fcourse of justice after he torched a
OL,9,Fcar involved in a fatal hit-and-run
OL,10,Fcollision which killed a 25-year-old
OL,11,Fman in Chorlton, Manchester.
OL,13,FDavid Toal, appearing for the defence,
OL,14,Fsaid his client had admitted to things
OL,15,Fthe prosecution had no evidence for,
OL,16,Fwhich showed he was taking
OL,17,Fresponsibility, and had planned to
OL,18,Fhand himself in to the police before
OL,19,Fhis arrest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
