OL,3,CDriver who 'recklessly' drove after
OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,FHe said: "An aggravating factor is
OL,7,Fthat he left the scene ` there is no
OL,8,Fexcuse for this.
OL,10,F"His explanation is that he panicked
OL,11,Fand that panic turned into shock when
OL,12,Fhe learned via social media that a
OL,13,Fyoung girl had lost her life."
OL,15,FFollowing the sentencing Lulu's
OL,16,Ffamily, from Burnley, Lancashire,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Lulu was our only child and the
OL,18,Fcentre of our world. Her joyful
OL,19,Fspirit, vivid imagination, and kind
OL,20,Fheart touched everyone who knew her.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUuD@^O]yD@GOU
