OL,3,CDriver who 'recklessly' drove after
OL,4,Ccocaine binge killing young girl jailed
OL,6,F"At just three years old, she brought
OL,7,Fmore light and love than we ever
OL,8,Fthought possible. Her life was full of
OL,9,Fpromise, and her loss is something we
OL,10,Fwill carry with us for the rest of our
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,FNo parent should ever have to witness
OL,14,Fthe death of their child. The impact
OL,15,Fof that single, devastating moment has
OL,16,Frippled through every part of our
OL,17,Fexistence, emotionally, physically,
OL,18,Fand financially.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
